representations that are optimised solely for classification accuracy, neglecting the distinct requirements of epistemic uncertai...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.21493", "source": "arXiv CS ML", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.21493v1/2605.21493v1/fig2_analysis_light.png", "score": 10}]}